works.description:
I have a DVD course called The Complete Muay Thai Home Study Course. I created this a few years ago and have been selling it online.
Recently it was brought to my attention that someone had uploaded the whole course to the web and the results are being displayed on GOOGLE VIDEOS.

So I looked and it is true - Google videos is displaying links to this unauthorized copyright violation of my work.

The link to see the listings that violate my copyright in Google is here:

http://www.google.com/#q=scott+sullivan+muay+thai&hl=en&prmd=ivnso&source=lnms&tbm=vid&ei=DvoVTrso8oywAt6mkDw&sa=X&oi=mode_link&ct=mode&cd=3&ved=0CA4Q_AUoAg&bav=on.2,or.r_gc.r_pw.&fp=f41fcb778c22f0cf&biw=1600&bih=698
